Package com.android

This covers polymorphic methods with regards to having methods that can take an interface reference as a parameter or a super class reference which can take many sub class objects. Use the Main to access all the Examples which contains the code that deals with this topic To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial
